    "asOf": "2020-06-30",
    "date": "2021-02-22T21:34:13Z",
    "text": "Health Care Prices Revealed and Information to Consumers Explained Transparency Act or the Health Care PRICE Transparency Act\n\nThis bill revises the format in which hospitals must list their standard charges for items and services to require that such lists are in a machine-readable format; it also revises the transparency requirements related to the costs of items and services for health insurance plans seeking certification as qualified health plans through insurance exchanges."
  },
